response.overview: The story of two of the greatest names in British aviation history, packed with precious archive film from their own vaults. Vickers and Supermarine were responsible for the EFB 1 and EFB 5 Gunbus, the R100 airship, Vimy Bomber, Valentia, Vildebeest, Stranraer flying boat, Spitfire, Wellington, Windsor, Viking, Viscount, Varsity, Valiant V-Bomber, VC10, Swift, and many others.
response.title: Vickers and Supermarine
